      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 14:21:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Robinhood 收购人工智能投资建议平台 Pluto</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/robinhood-acquires-ai-driven-investment-advice-platform-pluto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Robinhood Markets Inc. 同意收购人工智能研究平台 Pluto Capital Inc.，为零售经纪用户提供更加量身定制的投资策略和分析。]]></description>
